nd a US guideline on <em>Diagnosis and treatment of first metatarsophalangeal joint disorders </em>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/bunions/references/\">Vanore et al, 2003</a>].</p><!-- end field 596ed7b2-c2f9-476a-8c80-43c13d4c50bb --><!-- end item e876141f-afb5-4ca1-9c00-502437f60804 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}